{"type": "article", "id": 2235, "title": "不如怀念一下Bardot雪糕", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T23:29:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052222594gdplzM0YWfLO29B.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">来参观一个妖娆的、但是很可惜已经倒闭了的冰淇淋店。这家潮店充满了热烈的嘴唇，店面由品牌标志性的奶油色、深红色和黑色组成，雪糕们像珠宝一样被展示在玻璃柜台里。店家还会鼓励顾客与品牌标志性的红唇雪糕合影并上传到社交网络。店家的广告语就是“Love on a Stick”（冰棒上的爱），正如这些雪糕的标志性图案所暗示的，如果你想把雪糕带回家与爱人分享，没问题，独特的包装可以保证 8 小时不化。Bardot 的第一家店位于圣地亚哥，旗舰店则位于加州的亚凯迪亚。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135130EZwA6D8nP7CG03bQ.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"768\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135130zbF8cSTDREkMVCmo.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"451\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135130PLCwd93ap07bVzk4.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"457\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71461717\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135131r4CHPTb7ODx0XFEv.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"503\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78533333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}